{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-05-29-how-to-add-floating-text-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aHoisting! To add floating text in react js, you can use . It will add floating text in react js. Today, I am going to show you, how…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add floating text in react js, you can use <code class=\"language-text\">transform: translate(-50%, -50%) translateY(0);</code>. It will add floating text in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add floating text in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let’s start with the first step.</p>\n<h2>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h2>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 2: Import react component.</h2>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FloatingText <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./FloatingText'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./FloatingText.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 3: Create a Component.</h2>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;FloatingText text=\"Floating Text Example\" /></code> to add floating text in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FloatingText text<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Floating Text Example\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Define the add floating text example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">./FloatingText</code> and use <code class=\"language-text\">@keyframes float</code> to add floating text in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> FloatingText <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./FloatingText'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>FloatingText text<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Floating Text Example\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">./FloatingText.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./FloatingText.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">FloatingText</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> text <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"floating-text\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> FloatingText<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">'./FloatingText.css'</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.floating-text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \n    <span class=\"token property\">position</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">top</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">translate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> -50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">animation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> float 3s ease-in-out infinite<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  \n  <span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@keyframes</span> float</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">0%, 100%</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">translate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> -50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">translateY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token selector\">50%</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">translate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> -50%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">translateY</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>-20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;FloatingText/></code> and add floating text in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/98c9dd40c41e5151c7b0739bf6c64ea1/ec897/floating-text.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel